<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="character-page abyss-theme">
  <div class="container character-page-inner">
    <div class="character-cinematic-grid">
      <div class="character-poster">
        <div class="poster-coming-soon">Coming Soon</div>
        <div class="poster-placeholder">
          <div class="poster-placeholder-box">
            <div class="poster-placeholder-text">Meden Image Placeholder</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="character-copy">
        <div class="faction-badges">
          <span class="faction-badge faction-abyss">Abyss</span>
          <span class="power-badge">Enemy Force</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Meden</h1>
        <p class="character-subrole">Hostile Power</p>
        <p class="character-lead">
          Meden represents the hostile pressure rising against survival, order, and human stability.
          Their threat is active, invasive, and relentless.
        </p>

        <div class="character-panels">
          <div class="cinematic-panel">
            <h2>Description</h2>
            <p>
              Rather than a passive danger, Meden functions like a force pushing conflict forward — dark,
              predatory, and built to overwhelm.
            </p>

            <div class="power-list">
              <div class="power-item"><h3>Pressure</h3><p>Forces panic and collapse.</p></div>
              <div class="power-item"><h3>Predation</h3><p>Targets weakness without mercy.</p></div>
              <div class="power-item"><h3>Persistence</h3><p>Does not easily retreat.</p></div>
              <div class="power-item"><h3>Fear Spread</h3><p>Turns terror into a weapon.</p></div>
            </div>

            <div class="quote-panel">“Some enemies are not fought once. They are survived repeatedly.”</div>
          </div>

          <div class="cinematic-panel">
            <h2>Profile</h2>
            <div class="profile-list">
              <div class="profile-row"><span class="profile-label">Faction</span><span class="profile-value">Abyss</span></div>
              <div class="profile-row"><span class="profile-label">Role</span><span class="profile-value">Hostile Power</span></div>
              <div class="profile-row"><span class="profile-label">Power Theme</span><span class="profile-value">Predation / Pressure / Fear</span></div>
              <div class="profile-row"><span class="profile-label">Visual</span><span class="profile-value">Image Coming Soon</span></div>
              <div class="profile-row"><span class="profile-label">Background</span><span class="profile-value">Placeholder Active</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>